headline: Ecolab Launches Ecolab® CIP IQ™ and Announces Strategic Partnership With 4T2 Sensors
summary: ST. PAUL, Minn., September 26, 2025--Ecolab launches Ecolab® CIP IQ™ and announces strategic partnership with 4T2 Sensors as an innovative solution for the dairy and beverage industry.
